Class Room

java.lang.Object
  level.Room
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.event.KeyListener, java.util.EventListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
LargeRoom, LargeRoomKeyboard, LargeRoomSprite, PhysicsRoom, RoomA, RoomB, TestRoom, TiledRoom
public class Room
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.awt.event.KeyListener

Default Room class. This is the general, broad overview of a room. This particular type of room is used for full 2D freedom viewed in an orthagonal plane. Generally to use, extend a room, define your Key Board based actions, and you're all set.

Author:
Tim Butram, CJ Robinson
